IMAPStore personal-remote
Host imap.mailbox.org
User elmcat@mailbox.org
PassCmd "pass show email/mailbox.org/pass"
SSLType IMAPS

MailDirStore personal-local
Path ~/.mail/personal/
Inbox ~/.mail/personal/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel personal
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Patterns *
SyncState *

